      "comment": "SUNSET SNITCH (2) comes off an average performance last start when eighth at this track over 400m behind Fletcher Keeping (23.24) in a Grade 5. Was in the money the start prior. Better than the latest run and deserves another chance. RIPPIN' PIKE (3) overcame a collision in the run and scored in quick time latest (22.90) at this track over 400m in a Grade 6. Leading player again. HONG KONG PHOOEY (5) slotted in just off the lead from the wide draw last start and boxed on to finish third (22.72) at this track in a Grade 5/6 over 400m. Form from her last run is proving to be solid. Expected to feature again. COOL RUNNINGS (1) was out of the frame here most recently but can atone.",
